channel.title: New runescape Private server!
channel.description:
Hello, this is a new runescape private server, called [glow=red,2,300]Runitescape![/glow] We are always updating, and we are currently looking for admins/mods. Please check the site for more details. The site is [glow=red,2,300][url=http://www.Runitescape.co.nr]www.Runitescape.co.nr[/url][/glow]. Currently the server is down, but we are expecting to finish it VERY soon. Please just check the website for all the details. And if you need anything just post in the forums. Please sign up for our site! Thank you,
LJ
